data.description:
Turnkey home with a pool! LOW HOA ($80 a year)

Are you looking for a charming house to call home? Do you love to spend time outside floating in the pool? 

This could be the house for you.  With plenty of space to have family gatherings and entertain outside. This home sits right in town close to Wal-Mart, Home Depot, places to eat and schools.  You are right near SR23 if you need to travel to Jacksonville for work.  

This house checks all the boxes and is a must see! 

The back yard is fenced in with a screen around the pool.  

Schedule your showing!
